      "purposeInStoryline": "This opening lesson launches the entire Chemical Bonding sub-strand by presenting the anchoring phenomenon — the puzzling property contrasts of NaCl, graphite, aluminium, and diamond encountered in a Nairobi kitchen — and eliciting students' prior knowledge about atoms and electrons so that all future lessons are driven by genuine curiosity rather than content delivery.",
